264
00:13:49,579 --> 00:13:52,790
[BOTH gasp, laugh]

265
00:13:54,834 --> 00:13:56,294
All right, I've
taught you everything

266
00:13:56,336 --> 00:13:58,212
you need to know for the job.

267
00:13:58,254 --> 00:14:01,841
