277
00:14:22,904 --> 00:14:24,280
That's lazy.

278
00:14:24,322 --> 00:14:26,324
And it means you haven't
learned anything.

279
00:14:26,366 --> 00:14:29,369
Always keep learning
and you'll succeed!

280
00:14:29,410 --> 00:14:32,413
[BUNNY WORKERS grunting]

281
