291
00:15:05,655 --> 00:15:08,032
[MOMO]
No bunny for you, buddy.

292
00:15:08,074 --> 00:15:10,827
[TAHARA] Anyway, it's time to
review how to greet customers.

293
00:15:10,868 --> 00:15:11,661
[BOTH gasp]

294
00:15:11,702 --> 00:15:15,790
Give them a nice, firm bow,
then hold it for three seconds.

295
00:15:15,832 --> 00:15:18,668
And don't forget to smile
and speak clearly.

296
00:15:20,461 --> 00:15:22,922
Thank you so much for
coming to see us, hop!

297
00:15:22,964 --> 00:15:25,299
Welcome! Thank you
for joining us, bunny!

298
00:15:25,341 --> 00:15:26,843
Better!

299
00:15:26,884 --> 00:15:30,555
[TAHARA] Manami would look
so cute in a bunny suit.

300
00:15:30,596 --> 00:15:33,391
[MANAMI] Thanks for
coming to visit, big bro!

301
00:15:44,986 --> 00:15:47,947
[KUNAI] Allow me to welcome
you to Rabby, Madam.

302
00:15:51,534 --> 00:15:54,036
Well, aren't you
perfect, as usual!

303
00:15:54,078 --> 00:15:56,581
And, my. What a
charming little village!

304
00:15:56,622 --> 00:15:59,333
It looks different than the
rumors led me to believe.

305
00:15:59,375 --> 00:16:00,543
Oh, this is nothing.

306
00:16:00,585 --> 00:16:03,254
We've actually only just
started on these renovations.

307
00:16:03,296 --> 00:16:04,589
Give it another month or two

308
00:16:04,630 --> 00:16:07,800
and I guarantee you won't even
believe your eyes, Madam!

309
00:16:07,842 --> 00:16:09,427
Come back then and
you'll feel like you've

310
00:16:09,469 --> 00:16:11,804
died and gone
directly up to heaven.

311
00:16:11,846 --> 00:16:14,474
I have to admit, everything
you've shown me thus far

312
00:16:14,515 --> 00:16:16,934
has truly lived up to your word.

313
00:16:16,976 --> 00:16:19,020
[KUNAI]
It's this, right here.

314
00:16:19,061 --> 00:16:20,313
Some soap?

315
00:16:20,354 --> 00:16:23,941
[LUNA] Oh! That soap is
seriously the best thing, ever!

316
00:16:23,983 --> 00:16:26,277
It washes away dirt like
magic and leaves your skin

317
00:16:26,319 --> 00:16:28,613
so clean it sparkles!

318
00:16:28,654 --> 00:16:33,326
[SHRIMPFRY]
Magic. Sparkling, huh?

319
00:16:33,367 --> 00:16:35,244
[OONO]
That soap was a real hit!

320
00:16:35,286 --> 00:16:39,707
[SAMBO] Oh? So, this the village
you were talking about, Madam?

321
00:16:43,294 --> 00:16:44,754
[SHRIMPFRY]
Hold it right there, Gramps.

322
00:16:44,795 --> 00:16:45,838
[SAMBO]
Hmm?

323
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:48,549
I told you to wait
till I called for you.

324
00:16:48,591 --> 00:16:52,303
Well, you see, old folks like
me don't really like waiting.

325
00:16:52,345 --> 00:16:55,473
Madam, might I ask
who this gentleman is?

326
00:16:55,515 --> 00:16:56,516
If you must know,

327
00:16:56,557 --> 00:16:59,977
this old fool causing nothing
but trouble is Commander Sambo.

328
00:17:00,019 --> 00:17:03,147
As you can tell,
he doesn't see very well.

329
00:17:03,189 --> 00:17:05,399
I only brought him along
to show him a good time

330
00:17:05,441 --> 00:17:07,026
since the general
assumption is that

331
00:17:07,068 --> 00:17:09,529
he doesn't have many years left.

332
00:17:09,570 --> 00:17:12,823
You know, your mouth is just
as poisonous as ever, Madam.

333
00:17:12,865 --> 00:17:15,576
Don't you think you should
show your elders more respect?

334
00:17:15,618 --> 00:17:17,328
Speaking of mouths, hush.

335
00:17:17,370 --> 00:17:18,829
I'm sorry, sir.

336
00:17:18,871 --> 00:17:21,541
It sounds as if your
condition is quite serious.

337
00:17:21,582 --> 00:17:24,794
But perhaps we might be able
to do something to help you.

338
00:17:24,835 --> 00:17:28,297
Oh, I guess you must be the man
that Madam was talking about.

339
00:17:28,339 --> 00:17:30,508
As she said,
I'm Commander Sambo,

340
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:33,010
former retainer to Head
Soldier Marshall Arts.

341
00:17:33,052 --> 00:17:35,429
[OONO]
Arts? Who was that again?

342
00:17:35,471 --> 00:17:37,765
Oh? The renowned
Master Arts, you mean?

343
00:17:37,807 --> 00:17:40,893
This'll be fun. I can imagine
the tales of your exploits

344
00:17:40,935 --> 00:17:42,770
are great and plentiful.

345
00:17:42,812 --> 00:17:45,606
[SAMBO grunts]
Yes, but several years ago,

346
00:17:45,648 --> 00:17:49,110
a magical beast unfortunately
took both my eyes.

347
00:17:49,151 --> 00:17:50,778
I decided to go ahead and retire

348
00:17:50,820 --> 00:17:53,364
because I'm not much
use to anyone anymore.

349
00:17:53,406 --> 00:17:55,616
It must've been
really tough for you.

350
00:17:55,658 --> 00:17:56,742
It just so happens,

351
00:17:56,784 --> 00:17:59,537
one of the folks on my team
is an exceptional doctor.

352
00:17:59,579 --> 00:18:02,915
I'd be surprised if she couldn't
heal your eyes altogether.

353
00:18:02,957 --> 00:18:06,210
[gasps] You're not
jerking my chain, right?

354
00:18:06,252 --> 00:18:08,838
If you'd like, I'll take
you to her right now.

355
00:18:08,879 --> 00:18:11,424
[SAMBO] Please do! Even if
there's only a slim chance,

356
00:18:11,465 --> 00:18:14,385
this is more hope than
I've felt in a long time!

357
00:18:14,427 --> 00:18:16,971
Goodness, you're being
a bothersome old man.

358
00:18:17,013 --> 00:18:18,431
I'm very sorry about this.

359
00:18:18,472 --> 00:18:21,142
We definitely didn't mean
to make more work for you.

360
00:18:21,183 --> 00:18:23,811
It's no problem in
the slightest, Madam.

361
00:18:23,853 --> 00:18:26,731
Go ahead, Tahara,
you can take him inside.

362
00:18:26,772 --> 00:18:28,608
[TAHARA]
This way, Master Sambo.

363
00:18:28,649 --> 00:18:29,817
[SAMBO]
Thank you.

364
00:18:30,985 --> 00:18:31,777
[KUNAI]
Yu.

365
00:18:31,819 --> 00:18:33,487
[YU]
Yep, on it, Chief.

366
00:18:43,748 --> 00:18:45,374
Hello, welcome to you both.

367
00:18:45,416 --> 00:18:47,376
I'm glad to have you here.

368
00:18:48,377 --> 00:18:49,462
[SHRIMPFRY]
Look at this place.

369
00:18:49,503 --> 00:18:52,840
It feels like I've stumbled into
another world or something.

370
00:18:55,217 --> 00:18:56,344
Go on, Gramps.

371
00:18:56,385 --> 00:18:58,512
Won't you just have her
take a look already?

372
00:18:58,554 --> 00:19:00,348
Would you back off,
you meddling woman?

373
00:19:00,389 --> 00:19:02,433
I'm not likely to run
away from her, am I?

374
00:19:02,475 --> 00:19:05,478
Then get on with it,
you senile old man!

375
00:19:05,519 --> 00:19:08,898
[YU] Master Sambo, are you
ready to begin the examination?

376
00:19:11,067 --> 00:19:13,486
[SAMBO] I'd like to
say I'm sorry, first,

377
00:19:13,527 --> 00:19:15,905
for exposing you to
this awful thing.

378
00:19:15,946 --> 00:19:18,115
It's the venom of a Scarecrow.

379
00:19:18,157 --> 00:19:19,825
That's what did this to me.

380
00:19:19,867 --> 00:19:20,868
[YU]
Okay.

381
00:19:20,910 --> 00:19:23,579
[SAMBO] These days, I can only
see the outline of a person,

382
00:19:23,621 --> 00:19:25,414
and that's on a really good day.

383
00:19:25,456 --> 00:19:27,875
I can't tell you
how grateful I'd be

384
00:19:27,917 --> 00:19:29,293
if you could make it any better.

385
00:19:29,335 --> 00:19:31,212
Please, rest assured.

386
00:19:31,253 --> 00:19:32,463
In the country I came from,

387
00:19:32,505 --> 00:19:34,423
we have a medicine that
treats your symptoms

388
00:19:34,465 --> 00:19:36,676
and I think you're a
perfect candidate.

389
00:19:36,717 --> 00:19:39,804
[SAMBO gasps] My goodness,
you're really serious?

390
00:19:39,845 --> 00:19:42,348
Yes, please wait a moment.

391
00:19:47,103 --> 00:19:49,146
[KUNAI] Interesting,
she plans to cure him

392
00:19:49,188 --> 00:19:51,148
simply through medicine.

393
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:53,359
Now that I think about it,
she's probably right.

394
00:19:53,401 --> 00:19:56,862
It'd be a bit much to expose
them to Yu's Hand of God.

395
00:20:05,913 --> 00:20:07,248
All right, please look up.

396
00:20:07,289 --> 00:20:09,709
[SAMBO]
Like this?

397
00:20:09,750 --> 00:20:10,751
[SAMBO gasps]

398
00:20:14,004 --> 00:20:15,131
There you go.

399
00:20:15,172 --> 00:20:18,175
Now, I want you to
open your eyes real slow.

400
00:20:19,510 --> 00:20:23,222
[gasping]

401
00:20:23,264 --> 00:20:24,932
I can see everything!

402
00:20:24,974 --> 00:20:28,769
You did it! My eyes are
totally back to normal!

403
00:20:28,811 --> 00:20:31,397
Gramps, are you completely sure?

404
00:20:31,439 --> 00:20:32,773
Oh, Madam!

405
00:20:32,815 --> 00:20:35,317
You've fattened up a bit
since the last time I saw you!

406
00:20:35,359 --> 00:20:37,903
What have you been eating
to get yourself that big?

407
00:20:37,945 --> 00:20:40,865
[SHRIMPFRY] Would you kindly
shut up, you walking corpse?

408
00:20:40,906 --> 00:20:44,744
[SAMBO cries]

409
00:20:44,785 --> 00:20:47,788
I can hardly believe it!
Thank you so much.

410
00:20:47,830 --> 00:20:48,873
Now that you're healed,

411
00:20:48,914 --> 00:20:51,459
