your old post again.

412
00:20:51,500 --> 00:20:53,878
I'm sure Arts would be
delighted to see you.

413
00:20:53,919 --> 00:20:54,712
[SAMBO]
That's right!

414
00:20:54,754 --> 00:20:59,091
Lord Arts, your loyal Sambo
is coming back to serve you!

415
00:21:01,886 --> 00:21:05,723
Ah! I'm so sorry for having
caused such a big ruckus.

416
00:21:05,765 --> 00:21:08,934
