coins at the very least.

421
00:21:22,031 --> 00:21:23,616
So, you're sure?

422
00:21:23,657 --> 00:21:25,117
Of course, it's fine!

423
00:21:25,159 --> 00:21:27,036
That stubborn old blockhead
is indebted to me

424
00:21:27,077 --> 00:21:29,747
