and that's worth a lot.

425
00:21:29,789 --> 00:21:30,623
Truly.

426
00:21:30,664 --> 00:21:33,167
So much more than any number
of holy lambda coins,

427
00:21:33,209 --> 00:21:35,085
that's for certain.

428
00:21:35,127 --> 00:21:37,421
Well, if you insist.

429
00:21:37,463 --> 00:21:39,423
You know, I have a strong
feeling that you and I

430
00:21:39,465 --> 00:21:41,342
are going to become
great friends.

431
00:21:41,383 --> 00:21:45,012
What a coincidence!
I think so, too.

432
00:21:45,054 --> 00:21:50,226
[BOTH chuckling]

433
00:21:51,685 --> 00:21:53,270
[chuckles]

434
00:23:24,737 --> 00:23:26,322
[KUNAI]
Tell me, Tahara.

435
00:23:26,363 --> 00:23:27,615
How are you feeling about

436
00:23:27,656 --> 00:23:30,492
not being able to see
your little sister here?

437
00:23:30,534 --> 00:23:35,873
[TAHARA crying]
Manami... Manami!

438
00:23:35,915 --> 00:23:36,707
[KUNAI]
Uh...

439
00:23:36,749 --> 00:23:37,791
[TAHARA]
It's fine!

440
00:23:37,833 --> 00:23:40,377
With us running a business
like we're in the yakuza,

441
00:23:40,419 --> 00:23:43,339
it's really a lot better
that she's not around!

442
00:23:43,380 --> 00:23:45,549
[OONO sighs] You're always
such a nervous Nellie

443
00:23:45,591 --> 00:23:46,967
when it comes to your sister.

444
00:23:47,009 --> 00:23:49,303
[AKU] Demon Lord,
what's a nervous Nellie?

